name = "Oil Lamp and the Moth"
description = "A simple oil lamp used in their home in Calamba. By its light, Teodora Alonso told the story of the moth that flew toward the flame. From this story, Rizal learned that there are people willing to sacrifice themselves to reach the light of truth."
